ttps://media0.giphy.com/headers/theincredibledrpol/KbzRTokTb46K.jpg\",\"profile_url\":\"https://giphy.com/theincredibledrpol/\",\"username\":\"theincredibledrpol\",\"display_name\":\"The Incredible Dr. Pol\",\"name\":\"The Incredible Dr. Pol\",\"attribution_display_name\":\"The Incredible Dr. Pol\",\"description\":\"With 100,000 patients, Dr. Pol has seen it all. Specializing in large farm animals, this senior is anything but retiring as he takes an old school, no-nonsense approach to veterinary medicine. Unflappable and unstoppable, this Doc routinely puts in 14-hour days and is a legend in the community. In this series, we travel with Dr. Pol across rural Michigan to care for every family pet and head of livestock in need of his expertise.\",\"user_type\":\"partner\",\"facebook_url\":\"http://facebook.com/natgeowild\",\"instagram_url\":\"https://instagram.com/NatGeoWild\",\"twitter_url\":\"https://twitter.com/DrPol\",\"twitter\":\"DrPol\",\"tumblr_url\":\"\",\"website_url\":\"http://channel.nationalgeographic.com/wild/the-incredible-dr-pol/\",\"website_display_url\":\"channel.nationalgeographic.com\",\"is_public\":true,\"is_staff\":false,\"is_superuser\":false,\"is_verified\":true,\"suppress_chrome\":false},\"analytics_response_payload\":\"e=ZXZlbnRfdHlwZT1HSUZfU0VBUkNIJmNpZD03OTBiNzYxMWR4d2hsaHIyNGZydml6aTl2Mnh6OTU2bDhyNWE2bXNzODRhdTFncHUmZ2lmX2lkPWwwRzE4a1V2QnQ4QVp6czdDJmN0PWc\",\"analytics\":{\"onload\":{\"url\":\"https://giphy-analytics.giphy.com/v2/pingback_simple?analytics_response_payload=e%3DZXZlbnRfdHlwZT1HSUZfU0VBUkNIJmNpZD03OTBiNzYxMWR4d2hsaHIyNGZydml6aTl2Mnh6OTU2bDhyNWE2bXNzODRhdTFncHUmZ2lmX2lkPWwwRzE4a1V2QnQ4QVp6czdDJmN0PWc\u0026action_type=SEEN\"},\"onclick\":{\"url\":\"https://giphy-analytics.giphy.com/v2/pingback_simple?analytics_response_payload=e%3DZXZlbnRfdHlwZT1HSUZfU0VBUkNIJmNpZD03OTBiNzYxMWR4d2hsaHIyNGZydml6aTl2Mnh6OTU2bDhyNWE2bXNzODRhdTFncHUmZ2lmX2lkPWwwRzE4a1V2QnQ4QVp6czdDJmN0PWc\u0026action_type=CLICK\"},\"onsent\":{\"url\":\"https://giphy